<item>
            <title>[LU-18384] sanity test_57b: MDC before 990716 != after 990680</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18384</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/82a7f1ec-1aec-4c81-9abf-64b971919547&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/82a7f1ec-1aec-4c81-9abf-64b971919547&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_57b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 57b: default LOV EAs are stored inside large inodes === 07:03:53 (1722150233)
mcreating 100 files
total: 100 create in 0.15 seconds: 686.81 ops/second
Filesystem               1K-blocks   Used Available Use% Mounted on
10.240.44.49@tcp:/lustre  53855620 128920  50675932   1% /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-102vm6 lctl get_param -n osd*.*MDT0000.kbytesfree
opening files to create objects/EAs
Filesystem               1K-blocks   Used Available Use% Mounted on
10.240.44.49@tcp:/lustre  53855620 128964  50675356   1% /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-102vm6 lctl get_param -n osd*.*MDT0000.kbytesfree
 sanity test_57b: @@@@@@ FAIL: MDC before 990716 != after 990680 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es6_0/464&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es6_0/464&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-425.13.1.el8_7.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es6_0/680&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b_es6_0/680&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-425.19.2.el8_lustre.ddn17.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This fails occasionally since 2024-07-28 on various branches.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems possible that it may relate to xattrs/ACLs being created on the files, but I would expect the difference in allocated blocks in this case to be a multiple of 100 files created, instead of the 32 or 36 blocks reported.&lt;/p&gt;







